    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really? you think it's actually okay? i was a bit worried about the blood tests part though. if i'm feeling totally fine and my diet is consistent, do i really need to keep doing all those regular clinic visits and blood draws to check the levels? it seems like a lot of unnecessary testing if i'm just making a small adjustment",
